==French==
===Etymology===
From latin [[rubeus]]
===Prononciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ʀuʒ/
===Adjective===
'''rouge'''

# red ([[blood]] colour, [[coquelicot]] colour, [[fraise]] colour, etc.)
#: ''Le '''sang''' est rouge.'' - Blood is red.
# From an [[ideology]]  symbolised by a red flag ([[communism]], extrem left). 
#: ''L'armée rouge''

===Noun===
'''rouge'''
# The colour red, symbolising notably a critical point (ex.: ''être dans le rouge''), an [[interdict]] (ex.: ''passer au feu rouge''), the [[anger]] (ex.: ''voir rouge''), etc. The red is the one of three colours vidéo<!--sic--> of base (with the [[blue]] and the [[green]]).

